{"tha-ap8:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap8:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap8:0.3":"Upalittheraapadana ","tha-ap8:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap8:1.2":"sujato nama brahmano; ","tha-ap8:1.3":"Asitikotinicayo, ","tha-ap8:1.4":"pahutadhanadhannava. ","tha-ap8:2.1":"Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap8:2.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap8:2.3":"Lakkhane itihase ca, ","tha-ap8:2.4":"sadhamme paramim gato. ","tha-ap8:3.1":"Paribbaja ekasikha, ","tha-ap8:3.2":"gotama buddhasavaka; ","tha-ap8:3.3":"Caraka tapasa ceva, ","tha-ap8:3.4":"caranti mahiya tada. ","tha-ap8:4.1":"Tepi mam parivarenti, ","tha-ap8:4.2":"brahmano vissuto iti; ","tha-ap8:4.3":"Bahujjano mam pujeti, ","tha-ap8:4.4":"naham pujemi kincanam. ","tha-ap8:5.1":"Pujaraham na passami, ","tha-ap8:5.2":"manatthaddho aham tada; ","tha-ap8:5.3":"Buddhoti vacanam natthi, ","tha-ap8:5.4":"tava nuppajjate jino. ","tha-ap8:6.1":"Accayena ahorattam, ","tha-ap8:6.2":"padumuttaranamako; ","tha-ap8:6.3":"Sabbam tamam vinodetva, ","tha-ap8:6.4":"loke uppajji cakkhuma. ","tha-ap8:7.1":"Vittharike bahujanne, ","tha-ap8:7.2":"puthubhute ca sasane; ","tha-ap8:7.3":"Upagami tada buddho, ","tha-ap8:7.4":"nagaram hamsasavhayam. ","tha-ap8:8.1":"Pitu atthaya so buddho, ","tha-ap8:8.2":"dhammam desesi cakkhuma; ","tha-ap8:8.3":"Tena kalena parisa, ","tha-ap8:8.4":"samanta yojanam tada. ","tha-ap8:9.1":"Sammato manujanam so, ","tha-ap8:9.2":"sunando nama tapaso; ","tha-ap8:9.3":"Yavata buddhaparisa, ","tha-ap8:9.4":"pupphehacchadayi tada. ","tha-ap8:10.1":"Catusaccam pakasente, ","tha-ap8:10.2":"setthe ca pupphamandape; ","tha-ap8:10.3":"Kotisatasahassanam, ","tha-ap8:10.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","tha-ap8:11.1":"Sattarattindivam buddho, ","tha-ap8:11.2":"vassetva dhammavutthiyo; ","tha-ap8:11.3":"Atthame divase patte, ","tha-ap8:11.4":"sunandam kittayi jino. ","tha-ap8:12.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap8:12.2":"samsaranto ayam bhave; ","tha-ap8:12.3":"Sabbesam pavaro hutva, ","tha-ap8:12.4":"bhavesu samsarissati. ","tha-ap8:13.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap8:13.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap8:13.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap8:13.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap8:14.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap8:14.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap8:14.3":"Mantaniputto punnoti, ","tha-ap8:14.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap8:15.1":"Evam kittayi sambuddho, ","tha-ap8:15.2":"sunandam tapasam tada; ","tha-ap8:15.3":"Hasayanto janam sabbam, ","tha-ap8:15.4":"dassayanto sakam balam. ","tha-ap8:16.1":"Katanjali namassanti, ","tha-ap8:16.2":"sunandam tapasam jana; ","tha-ap8:16.3":"Buddhe karam karitvana, ","tha-ap8:16.4":"sodhesi gatimattano. ","tha-ap8:17.1":"Tattha me ahu sankappo, ","tha-ap8:17.2":"sutvana munino vacam; ","tha-ap8:17.3":"Ahampi karam kassami, ","tha-ap8:17.4":"yatha passami gotamam. ","tha-ap8:18.1":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap8:18.2":"kiriyam cintayim mama; ","tha-ap8:18.3":"Kyaham kammam acarami, ","tha-ap8:18.4":"punnakkhette anuttare. ","tha-ap8:19.1":"Ayanca pathiko bhikkhu, ","tha-ap8:19.2":"sabbapathissa sasane; ","tha-ap8:19.3":"Vinaye agganikkhitto, ","tha-ap8:19.4":"tam thanam patthaye aham. ","tha-ap8:20.1":"Idam me amitam bhogam, ","tha-ap8:20.2":"akkhobham sagarupamam; ","tha-ap8:20.3":"Tena bhogena buddhassa, ","tha-ap8:20.4":"aramam mapaye aham. ","tha-ap8:21.1":"Sobhanam nama aramam, ","tha-ap8:21.2":"nagarassa puratthato; ","tha-ap8:21.3":"Kinitva satasahassena, ","tha-ap8:21.4":"sangharamam amapayim. ","tha-ap8:22.1":"Kutagare ca pasade, ","tha-ap8:22.2":"mandape hammiye guha; ","tha-ap8:22.3":"Cankame sukate katva, ","tha-ap8:22.4":"sangharamam amapayim. ","tha-ap8:23.1":"Jantagharam aggisalam, ","tha-ap8:23.2":"atho udakamalakam; ","tha-ap8:23.3":"Nhanagharam mapayitva, ","tha-ap8:23.4":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham. ","tha-ap8:24.1":"Asandiyo pithake ca, ","tha-ap8:24.2":"paribhoge ca bhajane; ","tha-ap8:24.3":"Aramikanca bhesajjam, ","tha-ap8:24.4":"sabbametam adasaham. ","tha-ap8:25.1":"Arakkham patthapetvana, ","tha-ap8:25.2":"pakaram karayim dalham; ","tha-ap8:25.3":"Ma nam koci vihethesi, ","tha-ap8:25.4":"santacittana tadinam. ","tha-ap8:26.1":"Satasahassenavasam, ","tha-ap8:26.2":"sangharame amapayim; ","tha-ap8:26.3":"Vepullam tam mapayitva, ","tha-ap8:26.4":"sambuddham upanamayim. ","tha-ap8:27.1":"Nitthapito mayaramo, ","tha-ap8:27.2":"sampaticcha tuvam muni; ","tha-ap8:27.3":"Niyyadessami tam vira, ","tha-ap8:27.4":"adhivasehi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap8:28.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap8:28.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap8:28.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap8:28.4":"adhivasesi nayako. ","tha-ap8:29.1":"Adhivasanamannaya, ","tha-ap8:29.2":"sabbannussa mahesino; ","tha-ap8:29.3":"Bhojanam patiyadetva, ","tha-ap8:29.4":"kalamarocayim aham. ","tha-ap8:30.1":"Arocitamhi kalamhi, ","tha-ap8:30.2":"padumuttaranayako; ","tha-ap8:30.3":"Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap8:30.4":"aramam me upagami. ","tha-ap8:31.1":"Nisinnam kalamannaya, ","tha-ap8:31.2":"annapanena tappayim; ","tha-ap8:31.3":"Bhuttavim kalamannaya, ","tha-ap8:31.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap8:32.1":"Kito satasahassena, ","tha-ap8:32.2":"tattakeneva karito; ","tha-ap8:32.3":"Sobhano nama aramo, ","tha-ap8:32.4":"sampaticcha tuvam muni. ","tha-ap8:33.1":"Iminaramadanena, ","tha-ap8:33.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap8:33.3":"Bhave nibbattamanoham, ","tha-ap8:33.4":"labhami mama patthitam. ","tha-ap8:34.1":"Patiggahetva sambuddho, ","tha-ap8:34.2":"sangharamam sumapitam; ","tha-ap8:34.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap8:34.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap8:35.1":"Yo so buddhassa padasi, ","tha-ap8:35.2":"sangharamam sumapitam; ","tha-ap8:35.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap8:35.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap8:36.1":"Hatthi assa ratha patti, ","tha-ap8:36.2":"sena ca caturangini; ","tha-ap8:36.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap8:36.4":"sangharamassidam phalam. ","tha-ap8:37.1":"Satthi turasahassani, ","tha-ap8:37.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap8:37.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap8:37.4":"sangharamassidam phalam. ","tha-ap8:38.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap8:38.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap8:38.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap8:38.4":"amuttamanikundala. ","tha-ap8:39.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap8:39.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap8:39.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap8:39.4":"sangharamassidam phalam. ","tha-ap8:40.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap8:40.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap8:40.3":"Sahassakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap8:40.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap8:41.1":"Devarajena pattabbam, ","tha-ap8:41.2":"sabbam patilabhissati; ","tha-ap8:41.3":"Anunabhogo hutvana, ","tha-ap8:41.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap8:42.1":"Sahassakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap8:42.2":"raja ratthe bhavissati; ","tha-ap8:42.3":"Pathabya rajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap8:42.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap8:43.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap8:43.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap8:43.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap8:43.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap8:44.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap8:44.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap8:44.3":"Upali nama namena, ","tha-ap8:44.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap8:45.1":"Vinaye paramim patva, ","tha-ap8:45.2":"thanathane ca kovido; ","tha-ap8:45.3":"Jinasasanam dharento, ","tha-ap8:45.4":"viharissatinasavo. ","tha-ap8:46.1":"Sabbametam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap8:46.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap8:46.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap8:46.4":"etadagge thapessati. ","tha-ap8:47.1":"Aparimeyyupadaya, ","tha-ap8:47.2":"patthemi tava sasanam; ","tha-ap8:47.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","tha-ap8:47.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","tha-ap8:48.1":"Yatha sulavuto poso, ","tha-ap8:48.2":"rajadandena tajjito; ","tha-ap8:48.3":"Sule satam avindanto, ","tha-ap8:48.4":"parimuttimva icchati. ","tha-ap8:49.1":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap8:49.2":"bhavadandena tajjito; ","tha-ap8:49.3":"Kammasulavuto santo, ","tha-ap8:49.4":"pipasavedanattito. ","tha-ap8:50.1":"Bhave satam na vindami, ","tha-ap8:50.2":"dayhanto tihi aggibhi; ","tha-ap8:50.3":"Parimuttim gavesami, ","tha-ap8:50.4":"yathapi rajadandito. ","tha-ap8:51.1":"Yatha visado puriso, ","tha-ap8:51.2":"visena paripilito; ","tha-ap8:51.3":"Agadam so gaveseyya, ","tha-ap8:51.4":"visaghatayupayanam. ","tha-ap8:52.1":"Gavesamano passeyya, ","tha-ap8:52.2":"agadam visaghatakam; ","tha-ap8:52.3":"Tam pivitva sukhi assa, ","tha-ap8:52.4":"visamha parimuttiya. ","tha-ap8:53.1":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap8:53.2":"yatha visahato naro; ","tha-ap8:53.3":"Sampilito avijjaya, ","tha-ap8:53.4":"saddhammagadamesaham. ","tha-ap8:54.1":"Dhammagadam gavesanto, ","tha-ap8:54.2":"addakkhim sakyasasanam; ","tha-ap8:54.3":"Aggam sabbosadhanam tam, ","tha-ap8:54.4":"sabbasallavinodanam. ","tha-ap8:55.1":"Dhammosadham pivitvana, ","tha-ap8:55.2":"visam sabbam samuhanim; ","tha-ap8:55.3":"Ajaramaram sitibhavam, ","tha-ap8:55.4":"nibbanam phassayim aham. ","tha-ap8:56.1":"Yatha bhutattito poso, ","tha-ap8:56.2":"bhutaggahena pilito; ","tha-ap8:56.3":"Bhutavejjam gaveseyya, ","tha-ap8:56.4":"bhutasma parimuttiya. ","tha-ap8:57.1":"Gavesamano passeyya, ","tha-ap8:57.2":"bhutavijjasu kovidam; ","tha-ap8:57.3":"Tassa so vihane bhutam, ","tha-ap8:57.4":"samulanca vinasaye. ","tha-ap8:58.1":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap8:58.2":"tamaggahena pilito; ","tha-ap8:58.3":"Nanalokam gavesami, ","tha-ap8:58.4":"tamato parimuttiya. ","tha-ap8:59.1":"Athaddasam sakyamunim, ","tha-ap8:59.2":"kilesatamasodhanam; ","tha-ap8:59.3":"So me tamam vinodesi, ","tha-ap8:59.4":"bhutavejjova bhutakam. ","tha-ap8:60.1":"Samsarasotam sanchindim, ","tha-ap8:60.2":"tanhasotam nivarayim; ","tha-ap8:60.3":"Bhavam ugghatayim sabbam, ","tha-ap8:60.4":"bhutavejjova mulato. ","tha-ap8:61.1":"Garulo yatha opatati, ","tha-ap8:61.2":"pannagam bhakkhamattano; ","tha-ap8:61.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap8:61.4":"vikkhobheti mahasaram. ","tha-ap8:62.1":"Pannagam so gahetvana, ","tha-ap8:62.2":"adhosisam vihethayam; ","tha-ap8:62.3":"Adaya so pakkamati, ","tha-ap8:62.4":"yenakamam vihangamo. ","tha-ap8:63.1":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap8:63.2":"yathapi garulo bali; ","tha-ap8:63.3":"Asankhatam gavesanto, ","tha-ap8:63.4":"dose vikkhalayim aham. ","tha-ap8:64.1":"Dittho aham dhammavaram, ","tha-ap8:64.2":"santipadamanuttaram; ","tha-ap8:64.3":"Adaya viharametam, ","tha-ap8:64.4":"garulo pannagam yatha. ","tha-ap8:65.1":"Asavati nama lata, ","tha-ap8:65.2":"jata cittalatavane; ","tha-ap8:65.3":"Tassa vassasahassena, ","tha-ap8:65.4":"ekam nibbattate phalam. ","tha-ap8:66.1":"Tam deva payirupasanti, ","tha-ap8:66.2":"tavaduraphale sati; ","tha-ap8:66.3":"Devanam sa piya evam, ","tha-ap8:66.4":"asavati latuttama. ","tha-ap8:67.1":"Satasahassupadaya, ","tha-ap8:67.2":"taham paricare muni; ","tha-ap8:67.3":"Sayam patam namassami, ","tha-ap8:67.4":"deva asavatim yatha. ","tha-ap8:68.1":"Avanjha paricariya, ","tha-ap8:68.2":"amogha ca namassana; ","tha-ap8:68.3":"Duragatampi mam santam, ","tha-ap8:68.4":"khanoyam na viradhayi. ","tha-ap8:69.1":"Patisandhim na passami, ","tha-ap8:69.2":"vicinanto bhave aham; ","tha-ap8:69.3":"Nirupadhi vippamutto, ","tha-ap8:69.4":"upasanto caramaham. ","tha-ap8:70.1":"Yathapi padumam nama, ","tha-ap8:70.2":"suriyaramsena pupphati; ","tha-ap8:70.3":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap8:70.4":"buddharamsena pupphito. ","tha-ap8:71.1":"Yatha balakayonimhi, ","tha-ap8:71.2":"na vijjati pumo sada; ","tha-ap8:71.3":"Meghesu gajjamanesu, ","tha-ap8:71.4":"gabbham ganhanti ta sada. ","tha-ap8:72.1":"Cirampi gabbham dharenti, ","tha-ap8:72.2":"yava megho na gajjati; ","tha-ap8:72.3":"Bharato parimuccanti, ","tha-ap8:72.4":"yada megho pavassati. ","tha-ap8:73.1":"Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap8:73.2":"dhammameghena gajjato; ","tha-ap8:73.3":"Saddena dhammameghassa, ","tha-ap8:73.4":"dhammagabbham aganhaham. ","tha-ap8:74.1":"Satasahassupadaya, ","tha-ap8:74.2":"punnagabbham dharemaham; ","tha-ap8:74.3":"Nappamuccami bharato, ","tha-ap8:74.4":"dhammamegho na gajjati. ","tha-ap8:75.1":"Yada tuvam sakyamuni, ","tha-ap8:75.2":"ramme kapilavatthave; ","tha-ap8:75.3":"Gajjasi dhammameghena, ","tha-ap8:75.4":"bharato parimuccaham. ","tha-ap8:76.1":"Sunnatam animittanca, ","tha-ap8:76.2":"Tathappanihitampi ca; ","tha-ap8:76.3":"Caturo ca phale sabbe, ","tha-ap8:76.4":"Dhammevam vijanayim aham. ","tha-ap8:77.1":"Dutiyabhanavaram. ","tha-ap8:78.1":"Aparimeyyupadaya, ","tha-ap8:78.2":"patthemi tava sasanam; ","tha-ap8:78.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","tha-ap8:78.4":"santipadamanuttaram. ","tha-ap8:79.1":"Vinaye paramim patto, ","tha-ap8:79.2":"yathapi pathiko isi; ","tha-ap8:79.3":"Na me samasamo atthi, ","tha-ap8:79.4":"dharemi sasanam aham. ","tha-ap8:80.1":"Vinaye khandhake capi, ","tha-ap8:80.2":"tikacchede ca pancame; ","tha-ap8:80.3":"Ettha me vimati natthi, ","tha-ap8:80.4":"akkhare byanjanepi va. ","tha-ap8:81.1":"Niggahe patikamme ca, ","tha-ap8:81.2":"thanathane ca kovido; ","tha-ap8:81.3":"Osarane vutthapane, ","tha-ap8:81.4":"sabbattha paramim gato. ","tha-ap8:82.1":"Vinaye khandhake vapi, ","tha-ap8:82.2":"nikkhipitva padam aham; ","tha-ap8:82.3":"Ubhato vinivethetva, ","tha-ap8:82.4":"rasato osareyyaham. ","tha-ap8:83.1":"Niruttiya sukusalo, ","tha-ap8:83.2":"atthanatthe ca kovido; ","tha-ap8:83.3":"Anannatam maya natthi, ","tha-ap8:83.4":"ekaggo satthu sasane. ","tha-ap8:84.1":"Rupadakkho aham ajja, ","tha-ap8:84.2":"sakyaputtassa sasane; ","tha-ap8:84.3":"Kankham sabbam vinodemi, ","tha-ap8:84.4":"chindami sabbasamsayam. ","tha-ap8:85.1":"Padam anupadancapi, ","tha-ap8:85.2":"akkharancapi byanjanam; ","tha-ap8:85.3":"Nidane pariyosane, ","tha-ap8:85.4":"sabbattha kovido aham. ","tha-ap8:86.1":"Yathapi raja balava, ","tha-ap8:86.2":"nigganhitva parantape; ","tha-ap8:86.3":"Vijinitvana sangamam, ","tha-ap8:86.4":"nagaram tattha mapaye. ","tha-ap8:87.1":"Pakaram parikhancapi, ","tha-ap8:87.2":"esikam dvarakotthakam; ","tha-ap8:87.3":"Attalake ca vividhe, ","tha-ap8:87.4":"karaye nagare bahu. ","tha-ap8:88.1":"Singhatakam caccaranca, ","tha-ap8:88.2":"suvibhattantarapanam; ","tha-ap8:88.3":"Karayeyya sabham tattha, ","tha-ap8:88.4":"atthanatthavinicchayam. ","tha-ap8:89.1":"Nigghatattham amittanam, ","tha-ap8:89.2":"chiddachiddanca janitum; ","tha-ap8:89.3":"Balakayassa rakkhaya, ","tha-ap8:89.4":"senapaccam thapeti so. ","tha-ap8:90.1":"Arakkhatthaya bhandassa, ","tha-ap8:90.2":"nidhanakusalam naram; ","tha-ap8:90.3":"Ma me bhandam vinassiti, ","tha-ap8:90.4":"bhandarakkham thapeti so. ","tha-ap8:91.1":"Mamatto hoti yo ranno, ","tha-ap8:91.2":"vuddhim yassa ca icchati; ","tha-ap8:91.3":"Tassadhikaranam deti, ","tha-ap8:91.4":"mittassa patipajjitum. ","tha-ap8:92.1":"Uppatesu nimittesu, ","tha-ap8:92.2":"lakkhanesu ca kovidam; ","tha-ap8:92.3":"Ajjhayakam mantadharam, ","tha-ap8:92.4":"porohicce thapeti so. ","tha-ap8:93.1":"Etehangehi sampanno, ","tha-ap8:93.2":"khattiyoti pavuccati; ","tha-ap8:93.3":"Sada rakkhanti rajanam, ","tha-ap8:93.4":"cakkavakova dukkhitam. ","tha-ap8:94.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap8:94.2":"hatamittova khattiyo; ","tha-ap8:94.3":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","tha-ap8:94.4":"dhammarajati vuccati. ","tha-ap8:95.1":"Titthiye nihanitvana, ","tha-ap8:95.2":"marancapi sasenakam; ","tha-ap8:95.3":"Tamandhakaram vidhamitva, ","tha-ap8:95.4":"dhammanagaram amapayi. ","tha-ap8:96.1":"Silam pakarakam tattha, ","tha-ap8:96.2":"nanam te dvarakotthakam; ","tha-ap8:96.3":"Saddha te esika vira, ","tha-ap8:96.4":"dvarapalo ca samvaro. ","tha-ap8:97.1":"Satipatthanamattalam, ","tha-ap8:97.2":"panna te caccaram mune; ","tha-ap8:97.3":"Iddhipadanca singhatam, ","tha-ap8:97.4":"dhammavithi sumapita. ","tha-ap8:98.1":"Suttantam abhidhammanca, ","tha-ap8:98.2":"vinayancapi kevalam; ","tha-ap8:98.3":"Navangam buddhavacanam, ","tha-ap8:98.4":"esa dhammasabha tava. ","tha-ap8:99.1":"Sunnatam animittanca, ","tha-ap8:99.2":"viharancappanihitam; ","tha-ap8:99.3":"Anenjanca nirodho ca, ","tha-ap8:99.4":"esa dhammakuti tava. ","tha-ap8:100.1":"Pannaya aggo nikkhitto, ","tha-ap8:100.2":"patibhane ca kovido; ","tha-ap8:100.3":"Sariputtoti namena, ","tha-ap8:100.4":"dhammasenapati tava. ","tha-ap8:101.1":"Cutupapatakusalo, ","tha-ap8:101.2":"iddhiya paramim gato; ","tha-ap8:101.3":"Kolito nama namena, ","tha-ap8:101.4":"porohicco tavam mune. ","tha-ap8:102.1":"Poranakavamsadharo, ","tha-ap8:102.2":"uggatejo durasado; ","tha-ap8:102.3":"Dhutavadigunenaggo, ","tha-ap8:102.4":"akkhadasso tavam mune. ","tha-ap8:103.1":"Bahussuto dhammadharo, ","tha-ap8:103.2":"Sabbapathi ca sasane; ","tha-ap8:103.3":"Anando nama namena, ","tha-ap8:103.4":"Dhammarakkho tavam mune. ","tha-ap8:104.1":"Ete sabbe atikkamma, ","tha-ap8:104.2":"pamesi bhagava mamam; ","tha-ap8:104.3":"Vinicchayam me padasi, ","tha-ap8:104.4":"vinaye vinnudesitam. ","tha-ap8:105.1":"Yo koci vinaye panham, ","tha-ap8:105.2":"pucchati buddhasavako; ","tha-ap8:105.3":"Tattha me cintana natthi, ","tha-ap8:105.4":"tannevattham kathemaham. ","tha-ap8:106.1":"Yavata buddhakhettamhi, ","tha-ap8:106.2":"thapetva tam mahamuni; ","tha-ap8:106.3":"Vinaye madiso natthi, ","tha-ap8:106.4":"kuto bhiyyo bhavissati. ","tha-ap8:107.1":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap8:107.2":"evam gajjati gotamo; ","tha-ap8:107.3":"Upalissa samo natthi, ","tha-ap8:107.4":"vinaye khandhakesu ca. ","tha-ap8:108.1":"Yavata buddhabhanitam, ","tha-ap8:108.2":"navangam satthusasanam; ","tha-ap8:108.3":"Vinayogadham tam sabbam, ","tha-ap8:108.4":"vinayamulapassino. ","tha-ap8:109.1":"Mama kammam saritvana, ","tha-ap8:109.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap8:109.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap8:109.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap8:110.1":"Satasahassupadaya, ","tha-ap8:110.2":"imam thanam apatthayim; ","tha-ap8:110.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","tha-ap8:110.4":"vinaye paramim gato. ","tha-ap8:111.1":"Sakyanam nandijanano, ","tha-ap8:111.2":"kappako asaham pure; ","tha-ap8:111.3":"Vijahitvana tam jatim, ","tha-ap8:111.4":"putto jato mahesino. ","tha-ap8:112.1":"Ito dutiyake kappe, ","tha-ap8:112.2":"Anjaso nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap8:112.3":"Anantatejo amitayaso, ","tha-ap8:112.4":"Bhumipalo mahaddhano. ","tha-ap8:113.1":"Tassa ranno aham putto, ","tha-ap8:113.2":"candano nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap8:113.3":"Jatimadenupatthaddho, ","tha-ap8:113.4":"yasabhogamadena ca. ","tha-ap8:114.1":"Nagasatasahassani, ","tha-ap8:114.2":"sabbalankarabhusita; ","tha-ap8:114.3":"Tidhapabhinna matanga, ","tha-ap8:114.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap8:115.1":"Sabalehi paretoham, ","tha-ap8:115.2":"uyyanam gantukamako; ","tha-ap8:115.3":"Aruyha sirikam nagam, ","tha-ap8:115.4":"nagara nikkhamim tada. ","tha-ap8:116.1":"Caranena ca sampanno, ","tha-ap8:116.2":"guttadvaro susamvuto; ","tha-ap8:116.3":"Devalo nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap8:116.4":"agacchi purato mama. ","tha-ap8:117.1":"Pesetva sirikam nagam, ","tha-ap8:117.2":"buddham asadayim tada; ","tha-ap8:117.3":"Tato sanjatakopo so, ","tha-ap8:117.4":"nago nuddharate padam. ","tha-ap8:118.1":"Nagam dutthamanam disva, ","tha-ap8:118.2":"buddhe kodham akasaham; ","tha-ap8:118.3":"Vihesayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap8:118.4":"uyyanam agamasaham. ","tha-ap8:119.1":"Satam tattha na vindami, ","tha-ap8:119.2":"siro pajjalito yatha; ","tha-ap8:119.3":"Parilahena dayhami, ","tha-ap8:119.4":"macchova balisadako. ","tha-ap8:120.1":"Sasagaranta pathavi, ","tha-ap8:120.2":"aditta viya hoti me; ","tha-ap8:120.3":"Pitu santikupagamma, ","tha-ap8:120.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap8:121.1":"Asivisamva kupitam, ","tha-ap8:121.2":"aggikkhandhamva agatam; ","tha-ap8:121.3":"Mattamva kunjaram dantim, ","tha-ap8:121.4":"yam sayambhumasadayim. ","tha-ap8:122.1":"Asadito maya buddho, ","tha-ap8:122.2":"ghoro uggatapo jino; ","tha-ap8:122.3":"Pura sabbe vinassama, ","tha-ap8:122.4":"khamapessama tam munim. ","tha-ap8:123.1":"No ce tam nijjhapessama, ","tha-ap8:123.2":"attadantam samahitam; ","tha-ap8:123.3":"Orena sattadivasa, ","tha-ap8:123.4":"rattham me vidhamissati. ","tha-ap8:124.1":"Sumekhalo kosiyo ca, ","tha-ap8:124.2":"siggavo capi sattako; ","tha-ap8:124.3":"Asadayitva isayo, ","tha-ap8:124.4":"duggata te saratthaka. ","tha-ap8:125.1":"Yada kuppanti isayo, ","tha-ap8:125.2":"sannata brahmacarino; ","tha-ap8:125.3":"Sadevakam vinasenti, ","tha-ap8:125.4":"sasagaram sapabbatam. ","tha-ap8:126.1":"Tiyojanasahassamhi, ","tha-ap8:126.2":"purise sannipatayim; ","tha-ap8:126.3":"Accayam desanatthaya, ","tha-ap8:126.4":"sayambhum upasankamim. ","tha-ap8:127.1":"Allavattha allasira, ","tha-ap8:127.2":"sabbeva panjalikata; ","tha-ap8:127.3":"Buddhassa pade nipatitva, ","tha-ap8:127.4":"idam vacanamabravum. ","tha-ap8:128.1":"Khamassu tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap8:128.2":"abhiyacati tam jano; ","tha-ap8:128.3":"Parilaham vinodehi, ","tha-ap8:128.4":"ma no rattham vinasaya. ","tha-ap8:129.1":"Sadevamanusa sabbe, ","tha-ap8:129.2":"sadanava sarakkhasa; ","tha-ap8:129.3":"Ayomayena kutena, ","tha-ap8:129.4":"siram bhindeyyu me sada. ","tha-ap8:130.1":"Dake aggi na santhati, ","tha-ap8:130.2":"bijam sele na ruhati; ","tha-ap8:130.3":"Agade kimi na santhati, ","tha-ap8:130.4":"kopo buddhe na jayati. ","tha-ap8:131.1":"Yatha ca bhumi acala, ","tha-ap8:131.2":"appameyyo ca sagaro; ","tha-ap8:131.3":"Anantako ca akaso, ","tha-ap8:131.4":"evam buddha akhobhiya. ","tha-ap8:132.1":"Sada khanta mahavira, ","tha-ap8:132.2":"khamita ca tapassino; ","tha-ap8:132.3":"Khantanam khamitananca, ","tha-ap8:132.4":"gamanam tam na vijjati. ","tha-ap8:133.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap8:133.2":"parilaham vinodayam; ","tha-ap8:133.3":"Mahajanassa purato, ","tha-ap8:133.4":"nabham abbhuggami tada. ","tha-ap8:134.1":"Tena kammenaham vira, ","tha-ap8:134.2":"hinattam ajjhupagato; ","tha-ap8:134.3":"Samatikkamma tam jatim, ","tha-ap8:134.4":"pavisim abhayam puram. ","tha-ap8:135.1":"Tadapi mam mahavira, ","tha-ap8:135.2":"dayhamanam susanthitam; ","tha-ap8:135.3":"Parilaham vinodesi, ","tha-ap8:135.4":"sayambhunca khamapayim. ","tha-ap8:136.1":"Ajjapi mam mahavira, ","tha-ap8:136.2":"dayhamanam tihaggibhi; ","tha-ap8:136.3":"Nibbapesi tayo aggi, ","tha-ap8:136.4":"sitibhavanca papayi. ","tha-ap8:137.1":"Yesam sotavadhanatthi, ","tha-ap8:137.2":"sunatha mama bhasato; ","tha-ap8:137.3":"Attham tumham pavakkhami, ","tha-ap8:137.4":"yatha dittham padam mama. ","tha-ap8:138.1":"Sayambhum tam vimanetva, ","tha-ap8:138.2":"santacittam samahitam; ","tha-ap8:138.3":"Tena kammenaham ajja, ","tha-ap8:138.4":"jatomhi nicayoniyam. ","tha-ap8:139.1":"Ma vo khanam viradhetha, ","tha-ap8:139.2":"khanatita hi socare; ","tha-ap8:139.3":"Sadatthe vayameyyatha, ","tha-ap8:139.4":"khano vo patipadito. ","tha-ap8:140.1":"Ekaccananca vamanam, ","tha-ap8:140.2":"ekaccanam virecanam; ","tha-ap8:140.3":"Visam halahalam eke, ","tha-ap8:140.4":"ekaccananca osadham. ","tha-ap8:141.1":"Vamanam patipannanam, ","tha-ap8:141.2":"phalatthanam virecanam; ","tha-ap8:141.3":"Osadham phalalabhinam, ","tha-ap8:141.4":"punnakkhettam gavesinam. ","tha-ap8:142.1":"Sasanena viruddhanam, ","tha-ap8:142.2":"visam halahalam yatha; ","tha-ap8:142.3":"Asiviso ditthaviso, ","tha-ap8:142.4":"evam jhapeti tam naram. ","tha-ap8:143.1":"Sakim pitam halahalam, ","tha-ap8:143.2":"uparundhati jivitam; ","tha-ap8:143.3":"Sasanena virujjhitva, ","tha-ap8:143.4":"kappakotimhi dayhati. ","tha-ap8:144.1":"Khantiya avihimsaya, ","tha-ap8:144.2":"mettacittavataya ca; ","tha-ap8:144.3":"Sadevakam so tareti, ","tha-ap8:144.4":"tasma vo avirodhiya. ","tha-ap8:145.1":"Labhalabhe na sajjanti, ","tha-ap8:145.2":"sammananavimanane; ","tha-ap8:145.3":"Pathavisadisa buddha, ","tha-ap8:145.4":"tasma te na virodhiya. ","tha-ap8:146.1":"Devadatte ca vadhake, ","tha-ap8:146.2":"core angulimalake; ","tha-ap8:146.3":"Rahule dhanapale ca, ","tha-ap8:146.4":"sabbesam samako muni. ","tha-ap8:147.1":"Etesam patigho natthi, ","tha-ap8:147.2":"ragomesam na vijjati; ","tha-ap8:147.3":"Sabbesam samako buddho, ","tha-ap8:147.4":"vadhakassorasassa ca. ","tha-ap8:148.1":"Panthe disvana kasavam, ","tha-ap8:148.2":"chadditam milhamakkhitam; ","tha-ap8:148.3":"Sirasmim anjalim katva, ","tha-ap8:148.4":"vanditabbam isiddhajam. ","tha-ap8:149.1":"Abbhatita ca ye buddha, ","tha-ap8:149.2":"vattamana anagata; ","tha-ap8:149.3":"Dhajenanena sujjhanti, ","tha-ap8:149.4":"tasma ete namassiya. ","tha-ap8:150.1":"Satthukappam suvinayam, ","tha-ap8:150.2":"dharemi hadayenaham; ","tha-ap8:150.3":"Namassamano vinayam, ","tha-ap8:150.4":"viharissami sabbada. ","tha-ap8:151.1":"Vinayo asayo mayham, ","tha-ap8:151.2":"vinayo thanacankamam; ","tha-ap8:151.3":"Kappemi vinaye vasam, ","tha-ap8:151.4":"vinayo mama gocaro. ","tha-ap8:152.1":"Vinaye paramippatto, ","tha-ap8:152.2":"samathe capi kovido; ","tha-ap8:152.3":"Upali tam mahavira, ","tha-ap8:152.4":"pade vandati satthuno. ","tha-ap8:153.1":"So aham vicarissami, ","tha-ap8:153.2":"gama gamam pura puram; ","tha-ap8:153.3":"Namassamano sambuddham, ","tha-ap8:153.4":"dhammassa ca sudhammatam. ","tha-ap8:154.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap8:154.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap8:154.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap8:154.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap8:155.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap8:155.2":"buddhasetthassa santike; ","tha-ap8:155.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap8:155.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap8:156.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap8:156.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap8:156.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap8:156.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap8:157.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upali thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap8:158.1":"Upalittherassapadanam chattham. "}